1
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:14,066
(The All-devouring Whale: Homecoming)

2
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,633
(Episode 6)

3
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:49,433
Miss Gu.

4
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:51,266
It's been a while.

5
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,233
Duan Ye?

6
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,566
Why did you come here, too?

7
00:02:57,033 --> 00:02:58,900
(Duan Ye, from the Rakshas Sect)
Have you joined another sect?

8
00:02:59,833 --> 00:03:00,866
Who are you?

9
00:03:01,133 --> 00:03:01,866
Got lost.

10
00:03:02,166 --> 00:03:03,433
Don't disturb our hunting

11
00:03:03,966 --> 00:03:04,933
unless

12
00:03:05,333 --> 00:03:06,733
you also want to be our prey.

13
00:03:08,566 --> 00:03:09,966
You have become the master of the Lingxiao Pavilion?

14
00:03:10,166 --> 00:03:10,833
Stop chatting.

15
00:03:11,066 --> 00:03:12,366
My boss is talking to you.

16
00:03:13,666 --> 00:03:15,466
How dare you ignore us?

17
00:03:15,733 --> 00:03:16,800
Just die!

18
00:03:28,766 --> 00:03:29,600
It's Heimi.

19
00:03:29,833 --> 00:03:31,500
Great. Heimi is still alive!

20
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:34,033
I thought I'd never see you again.

21
00:03:41,633 --> 00:03:42,433
Heimi is...

22
00:03:43,833 --> 00:03:44,800
(Totem Enhancement)

23
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,600
Fight him out.

24
00:03:45,833 --> 00:03:46,533
Let's go.

25
00:03:46,533 --> 00:03:47,066
Right.

26
00:03:51,566 --> 00:03:52,266
Duan Ye!

27
00:04:24,866 --> 00:04:25,800
I yield.

28
00:04:35,866 --> 00:04:37,600
I... I survived.

29
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:48,600
Heimi.

30
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,600
Something is wrong with Heimi.

31
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:58,766
What happened to it?

32
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,766
As you can see,

33
00:05:01,133 --> 00:05:02,233
it survived

34
00:05:02,633 --> 00:05:03,833
and grew stronger.

35
00:05:04,866 --> 00:05:05,700
Because

36
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:09,033
I've joined a powerful sect.

37
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,666
Did they turn Heimi to that?

38
00:05:19,533 --> 00:05:20,333
Gu Ling.

39
00:05:21,333 --> 00:05:23,666
What's the point of struggling in the Lingxiao Pavilion?

40
00:05:24,733 --> 00:05:25,933
Join our Rakshas Sect.

41
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,500
I will be your introducer.

42
00:05:28,333 --> 00:05:31,633
Trust me, this is really the strong sect.

43
00:05:32,466 --> 00:05:33,466
No. Mister Duan.

44
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:35,200
Why not return to the Pavilion?

45
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,866
Since Mister Liu joined us,

46
00:05:36,866 --> 00:05:38,033
we have been recovering quickly.

47
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:41,300
Now I'm confident that we can rejuvenate the Pavilion.

48
00:05:43,633 --> 00:05:45,133
Rejuvenate the Pavilion?

49
00:05:47,233 --> 00:05:48,200
I'm not lying.

50
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:50,100
It only took one month

51
00:05:50,233 --> 00:05:51,766
to upgrade all our pets to the Soul-building Stage.

52
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,700
Look at Scent if you don't believe it.

53
00:05:54,366 --> 00:05:55,300
Come back, Mister Duan.

54
00:05:55,566 --> 00:05:56,500
We can make it.

55
00:05:58,900 --> 00:05:59,933
What a stupid woman.

56
00:06:01,766 --> 00:06:03,633
He's just a cheeky outsider!

57
00:06:03,933 --> 00:06:05,500
They're just some ridiculous pets!

58
00:06:06,066 --> 00:06:08,866
And look at your house-playing childishness!

59
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,900
Don't even imagine you can use them

60
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:13,266
to rejuvenate the Pavilion!

61
00:06:14,966 --> 00:06:16,566
But if you can come back...

62
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,433
Hold your tongue.

63
00:06:17,966 --> 00:06:20,066
You have no idea what you are talking about!

64
00:06:25,533 --> 00:06:26,900
I'm just casting pearls before swine.

65
00:06:31,466 --> 00:06:32,333
Mister Duan.

66
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,900
The Lingxiao Pavilion really needs you.

67
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,166
I'm no longer your fellow now.

68
00:07:00,733 --> 00:07:01,933
(Our ties were severed yesterday)
Our ties were severed yesterday.

69
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,233
(Our relationship is cut off today)
Our relationship is cut off today.

70
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,033
(Taking a new path alone)
Taking a new path alone,

71
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:09,233
(I won't look back)
I won't look back.

72
00:07:19,666 --> 00:07:21,400
Don't let me see that Mister Liu again

73
00:07:23,566 --> 00:07:25,433
because I will show him no mercy.

74
00:07:34,933 --> 00:07:36,166
Mister Duan.

75
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,266
I found the fourth one.

76
00:07:51,833 --> 00:07:52,866
I am strong indeed.

77
00:07:53,966 --> 00:07:54,766
Look, Thorn Back,

78
00:07:55,233 --> 00:07:56,300
I've got a question.

79
00:07:57,033 --> 00:07:58,100
(The sixth phase of the Soul-building Stage)
Why haven't you changed at all

80
00:07:58,133 --> 00:08:00,133
(The sixth phase of the Soul-building Stage)
after entering the Soul-building stage?

81
00:08:01,433 --> 00:08:02,100
In that case,

82
00:08:02,266 --> 00:08:03,633
no matter how strong I am,

83
00:08:03,633 --> 00:08:05,833
my charisma will be pulled down by you.

84
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:08,100
No.

85
00:08:08,366 --> 00:08:09,800
I want to change it.

86
00:08:12,266 --> 00:08:13,266
Why is it going there?

87
00:08:14,933 --> 00:08:15,800
Seems like nobody is around.

88
00:08:16,166 --> 00:08:17,166
Is it possible that others are avoiding me

89
00:08:17,166 --> 00:08:18,366
because I'm way too strong?

90
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:21,333
Then I will not

91
00:08:22,166 --> 00:08:22,833
stand on ceremony.

92
00:08:22,966 --> 00:08:23,400
Put it down!

93
00:08:24,966 --> 00:08:26,566
I found it first.

94
00:08:26,966 --> 00:08:28,000
So it's mine.

95
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,733
Give it to me

96
00:08:30,333 --> 00:08:31,700
before I beat the hell out of you.

97
00:08:35,666 --> 00:08:36,500
A kid?

98
00:08:38,866 --> 00:08:40,400
Boy, are you a contestant, too?

99
00:08:40,566 --> 00:08:41,866
Are you someone's relative?

100
00:08:42,133 --> 00:08:42,966
Don't be so rude!

101
00:08:43,833 --> 00:08:44,700
(The Master of the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple)
I am the master

102
00:08:44,733 --> 00:08:47,200
(The Master of the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple)
of the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple,

103
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,466
(Loong Nitian)
Loong Nitian!

104
00:08:50,933 --> 00:08:53,000
How did you come up with such a long name?

105
00:08:53,233 --> 00:08:54,566
How dare you mock me?

106
00:08:54,933 --> 00:08:57,000
Oh, sorry, Master Loong.

107
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,233
The spore touched my bracelet accidentally.

108
00:08:59,366 --> 00:09:00,066
How dare!

109
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,833
I told you it was mine.

110
00:09:01,833 --> 00:09:02,966
You want to be beaten up?

111
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,633
So, are you going to summon a white bunny

112
00:09:06,666 --> 00:09:08,233
or a tabby kitty?

113
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:11,533
You made me do this.

114
00:09:30,033 --> 00:09:31,033
What is going on?

115
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,266
Brother, look.

116
00:09:33,966 --> 00:09:34,666
What is that?

117
00:09:34,966 --> 00:09:35,466
That's...

118
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,866
Has someone summoned

119
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,300
an Emperor Grade spiritual pet?

120
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,300
(On the Emperor Grade, Azure Scale Loong, Phase: ? Stage: ?)

121
00:10:03,333 --> 00:10:04,000
Governor.

122
00:10:04,433 --> 00:10:05,733
It is an Emperor indeed.

123
00:10:05,833 --> 00:10:07,900
The trainer is a child from the Eighth Region.

124
00:10:08,166 --> 00:10:08,633
What?

125
00:10:09,066 --> 00:10:10,266
A child from our region?

126
00:10:10,366 --> 00:10:12,233
Is it Loong Nitian?

127
00:10:12,333 --> 00:10:13,100
How is that possible?

128
00:10:13,533 --> 00:10:15,200
(Signature: Loong Nitian)
Isn't that long name

129
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,266
(The World-shaking Super Invincible Temple)
the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple a joke?

130
00:10:17,633 --> 00:10:18,333
Besides,

131
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,666
no matter how hard a child cultivates,

132
00:10:20,733 --> 00:10:23,200
his Spiritual Pet Pool can't contain an Emperor.

133
00:10:23,266 --> 00:10:24,266
It is possible.

134
00:10:25,933 --> 00:10:27,333
Mister Bai, do you mean...?

135
00:10:27,666 --> 00:10:29,033
Spiritual Pet Accompany.

136
00:10:29,566 --> 00:10:30,666
Yes, Lord Lv.

137
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:34,233
If the trainer is talented enough when he is little,

138
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:36,000
he may put a pet embryo

139
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,633
into his Spiritual Pet Pool directly.

140
00:10:38,466 --> 00:10:38,866
Then

141
00:10:39,133 --> 00:10:40,500
it won't be restrained by the Pool's capacity.

142
00:10:40,966 --> 00:10:42,166
Are good things of this kind real?

143
00:10:43,133 --> 00:10:44,800
Why didn't Dad give me one?

144
00:10:45,133 --> 00:10:47,233
(One should be talented enough)
One should be talented enough.

145
00:10:47,466 --> 00:10:48,900
Why did you repeat it?

146
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:51,700
The conditions for the Spiritual Pet Accompany
are quite strict.

147
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:54,933
So the Accompany of an Emperor is almost a miracle.

148
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,033
The weird thing

149
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:59,400
is that such a powerful person is from a plain sect.

150
00:11:01,966 --> 00:11:03,166
I'm sure the lad

151
00:11:03,733 --> 00:11:05,333
has experienced something extraordinary.

152
00:11:09,033 --> 00:11:09,533
That...

153
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:11,000
That is...

154
00:11:11,833 --> 00:11:12,766
Spiritual Pet Accompany.

155
00:11:13,966 --> 00:11:15,266
You know so much.

156
00:11:15,866 --> 00:11:16,666
Are you jealous?

157
00:11:21,166 --> 00:11:22,566
The Spiritual Pet Accompany.

158
00:11:24,266 --> 00:11:24,833
I...

159
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:26,733
It's dead.

160
00:11:29,433 --> 00:11:30,833
Another one wasted.

161
00:11:30,933 --> 00:11:32,866
The embryo died again.

162
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,633
It died.

163
00:11:34,833 --> 00:11:36,200
We failed again.

164
00:11:36,533 --> 00:11:37,633
We failed again.

165
00:11:37,833 --> 00:11:39,900
I told you this child is not gifted enough.

166
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,733
Such a waste.

167
00:11:41,866 --> 00:11:43,100
Such a waste.

168
00:11:44,833 --> 00:11:47,866
You still won't give up after wasting so many resources?

169
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,866
Not gifted enough.

170
00:11:50,666 --> 00:11:52,666
Not gifted enough.

171
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:55,700
Not gifted enough.

172
00:11:59,000 --> 00:11:59,566
Father.

173
00:12:00,466 --> 00:12:01,000
Father.

174
00:12:03,066 --> 00:12:04,100
Forget it.

175
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,166
Too scared to speak?

176
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,666
Weren't you so aggressive just now?

177
00:12:26,566 --> 00:12:27,633
The Spiritual Pet Accompany

178
00:12:27,766 --> 00:12:28,566
is

179
00:12:29,533 --> 00:12:31,133
not a big deal.

180
00:12:32,466 --> 00:12:33,700
So arrogant.

181
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:36,533
Look out!

182
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,100
Then isn't it a one-horse race?

183
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,866
The Emperor will crush the others.

184
00:12:48,366 --> 00:12:48,866
Not really.

185
00:12:49,633 --> 00:12:51,233
There is a flaw in the Spiritual Pet Accompany.

186
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,400
(A Thesis on the Advantages, Disadvantages
and Their Influences of the Accompany Pets at Present)

187
00:12:52,433 --> 00:12:53,833
The development of the pet

188
00:12:53,866 --> 00:12:56,066
is closely bonded to the cultivation of its master.

189
00:12:57,066 --> 00:12:59,166
If the trainer doesn't cultivate hard,

190
00:12:59,633 --> 00:13:01,900
the pet's power will be limited, too.

191
00:13:03,233 --> 00:13:04,300
It's difficult for him

192
00:13:04,533 --> 00:13:06,800
to master an Emperor well enough at his age.

193
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:14,566
Where is that loong?

194
00:13:16,133 --> 00:13:18,000
It... fell over?

195
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,433
Stupid loong. How could you miss so closely?

196
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:24,933
Come on.

197
00:13:28,466 --> 00:13:29,033
Huh?

198
00:13:29,233 --> 00:13:30,800
How dare you blame my control?

199
00:13:31,066 --> 00:13:33,100
Isn't it because you didn't cooperate

200
00:13:33,133 --> 00:13:34,033
in the training?

201
00:13:35,233 --> 00:13:35,833
Stupid loong.

202
00:13:35,966 --> 00:13:37,200
How dare you snarl at me?

203
00:13:37,233 --> 00:13:38,433
Don't do it again!

204
00:13:39,233 --> 00:13:40,700
I'm surprised that they are fighting.

205
00:13:41,733 --> 00:13:42,900
Seems like it's hard for him

206
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,633
to master the Emperor.

207
00:13:45,233 --> 00:13:47,100
We stand a chance. Thorn Back.

208
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,633
On my mark.

209
00:13:49,133 --> 00:13:49,866
Ready.

210
00:13:52,333 --> 00:13:53,133
Right now!

211
00:13:55,166 --> 00:13:57,133
Taste this new skill developed by me.

212
00:13:57,366 --> 00:13:58,766
(Befalling Thorns)
Befalling Thorns.

213
00:13:58,866 --> 00:13:59,333
No.

214
00:13:59,433 --> 00:14:00,233
Scale, hurry.

215
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:01,033
Use Loong's Breath.

216
00:14:08,833 --> 00:14:09,333
No.

217
00:14:17,566 --> 00:14:19,466
Stupid loong, you've hit a turtle.

218
00:14:21,233 --> 00:14:21,966
Again?

219
00:14:26,166 --> 00:14:28,433
Scale, give me five points of your storage energy.

220
00:14:34,866 --> 00:14:35,766
Step aside!

221
00:14:38,966 --> 00:14:39,566
What happened?

222
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,633
How could a trainer have such power?

223
00:14:43,033 --> 00:14:44,700
You look confused.

224
00:14:44,866 --> 00:14:46,366
So you haven't witnessed this special skill

225
00:14:46,533 --> 00:14:47,600
of an Emperor.

226
00:14:49,533 --> 00:14:51,333
Let me enlighten you today.

227
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,700
It's useless.

228
00:14:58,466 --> 00:14:59,333
That's all?

229
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:04,966
Thorn Back, let's strike together.

230
00:15:06,866 --> 00:15:08,366
You should yield now.

231
00:15:08,966 --> 00:15:10,200
I've begun to feel bored.

232
00:15:13,866 --> 00:15:14,433
Once more.

233
00:15:16,166 --> 00:15:16,833
Once more.

234
00:15:17,866 --> 00:15:18,366
Once more.

235
00:15:20,766 --> 00:15:21,533
Why don't you

236
00:15:21,933 --> 00:15:23,333
just give up?

237
00:15:24,366 --> 00:15:25,633
It's not so easy

238
00:15:25,833 --> 00:15:27,566
to defeat us.

239
00:15:28,166 --> 00:15:29,466
You are wasting my time!

240
00:15:31,633 --> 00:15:33,566
Are we just wasting time?

241
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:35,333
The skill of the Emperor

242
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,700
should be limited.

243
00:15:43,233 --> 00:15:43,800
Scale.

244
00:15:44,033 --> 00:15:45,100
Give me ten points more.

245
00:15:45,333 --> 00:15:46,066
What?

246
00:15:49,666 --> 00:15:50,700
Thorn Back, run!

247
00:15:56,533 --> 00:15:58,066
Take this.

248
00:16:05,433 --> 00:16:06,966
It's finished easily.

249
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,500
Thorn Back.

250
00:16:09,566 --> 00:16:10,633
Now die!

251
00:16:11,966 --> 00:16:12,800
Stop!

252
00:16:22,433 --> 00:16:23,733
Come on, Dad.

253
00:16:24,033 --> 00:16:26,400
It's a nasty thing to break my fighting mood.

254
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,666
Loong Nitian's father?

255
00:16:32,633 --> 00:16:33,700
If I didn't stop you,

256
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,633
you would kill him.

257
00:16:36,733 --> 00:16:37,933
What are you talking about?

258
00:16:38,366 --> 00:16:40,233
I just wanted to scare him,

259
00:16:40,533 --> 00:16:41,433
and I wouldn't go too far.

260
00:16:41,766 --> 00:16:42,666
You wouldn't?

261
00:16:43,166 --> 00:16:45,233
You know what a racket it is to summon Scale?

262
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:48,233
I'm afraid it has drawn the attention
of all teams on this island already.

263
00:16:48,666 --> 00:16:49,633
Haven't you gone too far?

264
00:16:50,466 --> 00:16:52,366
That guy is too annoying.

265
00:16:52,466 --> 00:16:54,033
He also snatched my spore.

266
00:17:01,133 --> 00:17:02,233
Tyke.

267
00:17:02,733 --> 00:17:04,466
You've seen the huge gap between you and us.

268
00:17:05,166 --> 00:17:05,966
Yield now

269
00:17:06,433 --> 00:17:07,633
and I'll spare your life.

270
00:17:08,466 --> 00:17:10,200
Otherwise...

271
00:17:12,533 --> 00:17:13,866
I'd rather die than yield.

272
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:20,966
This is thorny.

273
00:17:21,166 --> 00:17:22,466
I said we wouldn't kill him first.

274
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,600
So he knows my bottom line.

275
00:17:23,933 --> 00:17:25,566
You look too simple and honest

276
00:17:25,666 --> 00:17:26,866
to pretend to be a bad guy.

277
00:17:30,066 --> 00:17:31,733
Whatever. Don't waste time.

278
00:17:32,133 --> 00:17:33,500
Let's go collect scores.

279
00:17:34,133 --> 00:17:35,433
How many scores have you got?

280
00:17:35,533 --> 00:17:36,066
One.

281
00:17:36,433 --> 00:17:36,833
Look.

282
00:17:45,266 --> 00:17:46,366
Forget it.

283
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:54,866
Impressive!

284
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:56,200
That's my son.

285
00:17:56,933 --> 00:17:58,133
How did you make it?

286
00:18:01,033 --> 00:18:02,100
Stop rubbing my hair.

287
00:18:02,133 --> 00:18:03,400
You are messing up my hairstyle.

288
00:18:03,866 --> 00:18:05,266
Because you horsed around.

289
00:18:05,300 --> 00:18:06,900
What was the big deal?

290
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,233
It was so close.

291
00:18:30,366 --> 00:18:31,666
I dodged that strike luckily.

292
00:18:31,866 --> 00:18:32,766
Did you get hurt?

293
00:18:33,033 --> 00:18:33,866
What happened to your foot?

294
00:18:34,333 --> 00:18:35,000
Just a scratch.

295
00:18:35,266 --> 00:18:35,733
Don't worry.

296
00:18:36,066 --> 00:18:37,666
I told you to practice mastering more.

297
00:18:37,900 --> 00:18:39,033
But you would not listen.

298
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:40,700
I won him anyway.

299
00:18:43,933 --> 00:18:44,666
Loong Nitian!

300
00:18:47,666 --> 00:18:48,766
I am Cheng Xi,

301
00:18:49,966 --> 00:18:51,266
and I will defeat you one day.

302
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:58,933
Cheng Xi?

303
00:19:01,533 --> 00:19:02,033
I'll remember you.

304
00:19:06,233 --> 00:19:07,433
Whenever you're ready.

305
00:19:08,233 --> 00:19:09,233
(Lonog Nitian, the Master)

306
00:19:09,266 --> 00:19:11,533
(The World-shaking Super Invincible Temple)